name: prodMKLeft_unit_equiv
declaration:
/-- Measurable equivalence with the product with the one-point space `Unit`.-/
def prodMKLeft_unit_equiv (α : Type u_4) [MeasurableSpace α] : Unit × α ≃ᵐ α

name: prodAssoc
declaration:
/-- Canonical bijection between `(α × β) × γ` and `α × β × γ`. -/
def prodAssoc {α : Type u_1} {β : Type u_2} {γ : Type u_3} : {x : MeasurableSpace α} → {x_1 : MeasurableSpace β} → {x_2 : MeasurableSpace γ} → (α × β) × γ ≃ᵐ α × β × γ
